- Brand new state of the art purpose built childcare investment

- High quality boutique family operator & childcare developer / builder of 20+ year experience

- Nino Early Learning Adventures with strong Melbourne network of 13 trading and forthcoming centres

- New 20 year lease with 10 year option, plus 3% annual increases and 6 month bank guarantee

- Income: $488,000 pa* + GST

- Permit: Childcare centre for 122 children

- Land area/zoning: 1,161sqm* / Public use zone PUZ4

- Building area: 913sqm*

- Status: Construction nearing completion - Imminent opening August 2017 (strong registrations of interest)

- Undervalued asset class experiencing exceptional demand due to Melbourne's booming population growth

- Investment sector supported by $37billion investment by Federal Government over the next 4 years & subsidies for childcare centre parents

- Attractive depreciation benefits

- Strategic catchment location

*approx.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to present 597 Gilbert Road, Preston, for lease and available now.

Set on a large site of 233sqm*, this property provides a rare opportunity to lease a blank canvass and turn it into something you can call your own.

The subject property is ideally located on the western side of Gilbert Road, between Union and McNamara Streets, only 9kms* north-east of Melbourne's CBD. It enjoys a unique aspect located directly opposite J S Grey Reserve.

597 Gilbert Road is strategically positioned in proximity to Regent Village and High Street's well-regarded retail strip which incorporates a vast array of national tenants including Woolworths, Aldi and the Preston Market.

Additional features include:
+ Functional single level shop/office of 80sqm*
+ Land area: 233sqm*
+ Huge rear yard/carpark
+ Valuable landholding of 233sqm*
+ Generous rear access
+ Zoned Commercial 1
+ Available now
+ Suit a wide range of uses (STPA)
+ Flexible lease terms and incentives

For further details on this property or your commercial property needs, please contact the marketing agent, Guy Naselli 0413 750 744

*approx.

Located adjacent to large, national tenants, the building has immediate access to Bell Street and other major arterials.

Positioned 11km* from Melbourne's CBD and situated in one of the most tightly held commercial precincts in Victoria.

- Total land area: 4,268sqm*
- Building area: 2,575sqm*
- 8 on site car parks
- Industrial 3 zone
- 7 roller shutter doors
